In this example I built upon 000-03
and added some query parameters as well to my REST JX-RX service.

The service can be tested at:

http://mperdikeas:8080/helloJersey/rest/actions/say/fuck_you/to/her
http://mperdikeas:8080/helloJersey/rest/actions/do/kill/to/George_Bush
http://mperdikeas:8080/helloJersey/rest/actions/browserInfo
http://mperdikeas:8080/helloJersey/rest/actions?a=23&b=25&c=2344  


(as you can see from the last example, extra query parameters do no hurt)